text: www. popsugar. com / Wednesday, 24 January 2018 14 : 54 : 03 While we were gawking over the Kardashian - Jenner Calvin Klein ad, eagle - eyed Kylie fans zoomed in on the sister's biggest feature. Or, in this case, Kylie's famous lips were much smaller than expected. Given that the 20 - year - old partly made a name for herself due to her lip injections, it was a little surprising to see her pout less plumped up. Twitter was quick to point out this could be the case because Kylie is rumored to be pregnant and therefore could be unable to get the procedure.
